    "Following the incident in question, the lot of us met with the rest of the temple priests before revisiting the scene of the crime."


translate English day10_8bf5db7f:


    et "However, by the time we got there, the remaining bodies were nothing more than scattered debris, {w}the dissolved remains no longer recognizable as once being human."


translate English day10_0bdcd464:



    nvl clear
    "\n Many of the priests scavenged the area for most of the day, but all they found was the certain fact that those once humans were gone, absolutely and completely."


translate English day10_da67b101:


    "Thus making the caskets nothing more than a symbol in keeping with the spirit of tradition. {w}But I have no desire to toss holy water on an empty coffin."


translate English day10_440c4c31:


    "And so I simply looked up at the girl who now exists only within the boundaries of that small picture frame, {w}letting the emptiness that comes with the loss of life wash over me."


translate English day10_656e385d:


    "Various memories flash before my eyes, though none linger long, quickly fading into the darkness of my mind."


translate English day10_e76bfcb5:


    "I've yet to shed even a single tear despite how dry my eyes are, having seemingly forgotten how to blink."


translate English day10_d8616335:


    et "It's still hard to believe that I lost so much over the course of a single morning."


translate English day10_10168666:



    nvl clear
    "\n Bishop Erzsebet did not show up for the funeral. {w}To be honest, I've been going out of my way to avoid him ever since the accident happened."


translate English day10_b28186fc:


    "After it happened, the first thing I worried about was how they might react."


translate English day10_e0715e21:


    "Having such a strong family bond, I knew they'd be pissed, holding me accountable for everything that occured."


translate English day10_f68279b6:


    "But that's just how I assumed things would go. {w}Time passed and no one approached me, perhaps evidence of their inability to think straight due to the sudden nature of such a freak accident"


translate English day10_20f679dd:


    "Of course I'm heartbroken, but to people like them, my sadness is nothing more than a joke, forgotten in an instant. {w}And I hate that."


translate English day10_825dc959:


    et "In the end, I'm nothing more than an outsider, the one-sided distance on my part simply a stupid misunderstanding."


